                <h2>Welcome to the Young Bankers Association</h2>
                <p>“Young Bankers Connect” is a nonprofit organization that reunites a network of executive from various industries in the aim to raise funds to the benefit of humanity and environmental causes.
Our aim is to give a new ethic to the financial sector because like modern economists, we believe that altruism is a necessity in economy. We believe that redistributing capital in a sustainable way creates growth, progress and benefits to all.</br> </p>
          <p>  At YBC we share common values such as spelled out in the charter. So that this association can thrive, we need to make our work a fusion of talent and competences as well as compassion and altruism of our members and their collaboration to form and fund and support specific associations. </br></p>
     
 

