            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2 class="page-header">Endorse to the Charter</h2>
                <p>Want to join our community? Agree with our values? Are you ready to invest in sustainable projects? </p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="the_charter.html">Click here and join us!</a>
            </div>
<div class="col-md-8">
                <h2 class="page-header">Our Vision</h2>
                <p>Integrity and consideration for each other is fundamental in economics. We have to be concerned by one another so altruism is now more than ever a necessity in order to give each one of us the opportunity to thrive. Unconditional level of cooperation and solidarity should be an essential asset in our industry. 
“Young Bankers Connect” believes that sharing data, resources and expanding network is constructive to the benefit of all instead of encouraging company or individual competition. That way, we work together in a win-win situation, and within a network where everyone is considered and distinguished as a sensible human being. Not only by their professional success. 
 
</p>
            </div>
           
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <h2 class="page-header">Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Give a new ethics to the banking sector and - as world reknown monk Matthieu Ricard states- put compassion in action by redistributing the capital to sustainable causes. We need to bring a gap between rich and poor in order to contribute to growth in a fairer way. Therefore, our association would serve as a positive grant in which one could invest in. 
The YBC mission is to gather each one’s competencies to generate funds in order to support important causes, and to scale to respond to the vast needs across the world. And within that gathering, creating a club, a group that represent the values of our Charter, that agrees that altruism is a <strong>necessity</strong>.
</p>
